# Node
**/node_modules
**/.pnpm-store
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage

# Python
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.egg-info
**/.venv
**/venv
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.pytest_cache
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov

# Git
**/.git
**/.gitignore

# Secrets — never bake into image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Docs / tests (not needed at runtime)
# README.md is intentionally NOT excluded — every pyproject.toml references
# it as the package readme; hatchling errors if the file is missing during
# the editable install in the api/auditor deps stages.
**/CHANGELOG.md
**/CONTRIBUTING.md
**/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
**/docs
**/tests
**/evals

# Docker files themselves
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/.dockerignore

# Claude / private
**/.claude
**/.private
**/decisions

# Logs
**/*.log
